{"tid":2138324,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"舉報會員130563專登改名後去多次重複post","createTime":"2020-08-03T13:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T11:00:37.000Z","uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7274f8cbdb4270e3f652027610579ec8f426cc44","tid":2138324,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iWLsMOn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiWLsMOn.png&h=83f6c14a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/130563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/130563</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/search?q=海賊王&amp;sort=desc_create_time&amp;type=thread\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/search?q=海賊王&amp;sort=desc_create_time&amp;type=thread</a>"},{"pid":"d273889378c971ecf4542327fc70d4bace7b03c8","tid":2138324,"uid":2857,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:39:55.000Z","msg":"樓上係on9仔"},{"pid":"934692eee3b86d8de9af0ff8e62dc2e4264a7e6f","tid":2138324,"uid":135110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:41:00.000Z","msg":"5毛 遠阪凜#3020 手持至少6個連登帳號,請admin跟進<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1291657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n熱烈恭賀牙井當選區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1751830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1751830</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好回覆呢個post，唔好幫佢賺錢！<br />\n會員#3020遠阪凜係連登知名過街老鼠及5毛！<br />\n牽涉多單竊取會員資料，宣傳特定網頁！<br />\n多次洗版式帶風向，包括慌稱自己是一名抗爭者，扮演手足！<br />\n混淆視聽話自己要參選區議會，以及不斷活躍於政治帖意圖帶風向！<br />\n甚至協助ddos連登等行為，已經係證據確鑿！<br />\n鬼知佢背後有咩動機，總之block咗佢就最一了百了！<br />\n請大家留意！"},{"pid":"ca2cf6bfa0d75c3dbc110abd37281c38b5b79274","tid":2138324,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"食屎狗又洗版屈毛,戀童狗"},{"pid":"c2167e97ac4734fdc3fd2e608f49137958a4fbab","tid":2138324,"uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"樓下係husky bot"},{"pid":"6ab7e08d350d6d81adf6354ffd056faeea351025","tid":2138324,"uid":1402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2167e97ac4734fdc3fd2e608f49137958a4fbab","tid":2138324,"uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"樓下係husky bot"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"21fe269cb0306adfb380dbf1155b96c91ee08a25","tid":2138324,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6ab7e08d350d6d81adf6354ffd056faeea351025","tid":2138324,"uid":1402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2167e97ac4734fdc3fd2e608f49137958a4fbab","tid":2138324,"uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"樓下係husky bot"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"hi"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:55:17.000Z","msg":"你哋宜家屌鳩台主嗰啲嘢......<br />\n<br />\n我早你哋七年前已經屌緊啦！<br />\n<br />\n成班語無倫次，搞利益集團，講說話冇文化冇內涵，拍埋啲嘢冇公共性。<br />\n<br />\n我睇住動物台由型轉柒，咁多年講咗不下十次。<br />\n<br />\n不過台主柒還柒呀，你宜家話人係政府喉舌，又有冇證據呀？<br />\n<br />\n當年高登連登仲有人撐楊岳橋，但台主係公開支持梁天琦架喎！<br />\n<br />\n你有權覺得檢舉bam圖係不道德，但係你哋憑咩話人暗共呀？<br />\n<br />\n你哋係咪熱狗嚟㗎？<br />\n<br />\n有咩證據可以證明到佢哋係政府嘅契弟呀？<br />\n<br />\n隔離仲有個KOL叫你做兄弟，但係唔理你生死。<br />\n<br />\n被你問多兩句就發脾氣屌鳩你，到宜家都冇回應又唔道歉。<br />\n<br />\n佢啲言行有曬記錄同證據㗎喎！<br />\n<br />\n結果隔一排出返嚟試水溫做直播，大家又可以繼續睇得好開心，留言話達朝萬歲，<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，有個毒撚柒頭。<br />\n<br />\n我屌咗佢地啲柒嘢好多年，但係你地之前又唔敢join我一齊屌。<br />\n<br />\n結果宜家冇證據，你哋又突然話人係政府喉舌，係暗共。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家就要一齊對抗暗共，抵制台主<br />\n<br />\n你哋條標準點訂架？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想叫大家停手，唔好殺人。<br />\n<br />\n我只係想指出你地公私不分，出師無名。<br />\n<br />\n如果你哋要加入我，一齊對抗快餐文化，對抗大台文化。<br />\n<br />\n我就無任歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n但如果你要夾硬作藉口，屈鳩任何人係暗共。<br />\n<br />\n我就絕不能苟同，此風不可長！<br />\n<br />\n就算你話達哥係暗共，我都係一樣咁話。<br />\n<br />\n係咪你唔妥佢，就可以屈佢係鬼？<br />\n<br />\n咁仲係唔係不分化不割蓆？<br />\n<br />\n話人係鬼，好大指控喎，究竟宜家係咪有證據呀？"},{"pid":"9803fb871aa5f9a1df3a5cc67d61f10a71c5ae96","tid":2138324,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:01:48.000Z","msg":"5毛狗#3020 見人貼正體中文多人睇又發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093fc8c1f9c5731900a482b8a43e2303b8652ad8","tid":2138324,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"18963c9c0cd7b24989eda2d063cfad4775814357","tid":2138324,"uid":2857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e51e6453422682853b3a6e1185f8ed8a805affd","tid":2138324,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"國安法打手5毛遠阪凜 #3020<br />\n蘋果：國安法7月1生效 駐港國家安全公署同步成立 部份罪行最高判終身監禁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ayNkLrV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ayNkLrV</a><br />\n#13 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b8ee8b458b670249a12df0e6d1964cff8405bd2","tid":2138324,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:15:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連<br />\n登<br />\n日<br />\n報<br />\n｜<br />\n支<br />\n持<br />\n獨<br />\n裁<br />\n政<br />\n權<br />\n者<br />\n，<br />\n無<br />\n權<br />\n享<br />\n有<br />\n言<br />\n論<br />\n自<br />\n由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNv9jui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNv9jui.jpg&h=2d820456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請<br />\n問<br />\n遠阪凜<br />\n(狗隻#3020)<br />\n你<br />\n屙<br />\n尿<br />\n嗰<br />\n陣<br />\n起<br />\n左<br />\n腳<br />\n定<br />\n右<br />\n腳<br />\n?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2149465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2149465</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"5094fcde421ad01c32afd1380ea71082077de36d","tid":2138324,"uid"